channel.title: Moparscape keylogger?
channel.description:
Well, i was on msn and my mate sended me this:
Sorry i infected some of the people that used my webclient with a keylogger
I have moparisthebest's permission to post here
to remove it go into my computer then #:\windows\system32\sys32\
open a command prompt and type tskill XXFS
then delete everything in the windows\system32\sys32 folder
OR if tskill doesnt work
start in safe mode and delete everything in the windows\system32\sys32 folde
He says it comes somewhere from this forums, and hes dutch so he cant make this all up, Could som1 explain this??

item.title: Moparscape keylogger?
item.dc:creator: @WiZzLe WiZzLe
item.description:
@WiZzLe wrote:

The Official MoparScape WebClient is NOT infected with a keylogger. However, a member here called ‘aaa801’ infected his webclient with a keylogger. He infected it a few months back and did not mean to do it. Right now, his nor MoparScape’s webclient is infected with a keylogger.

Read about the keylogger here - http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,92342.0.html

Read full topic
